Image Expiration / Retention Extension – Cohesity (Exception Summary)

Purpose:
To extend snapshot retention beyond standard policy based on operational or compliance requirements.

Summary:
Cohesity allows modification of snapshot expiry at the snapshot level. Extending expiry delays deletion and acts as an approved exception to standard retention policies.

